{"word":"G4768 - στυγνάζω - stygnázō - stoog-nad'-zo - Lower","slug":"G4768","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στυγνάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>stygnázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>stoog-nad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Lower"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03C5;&#x03B3;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - stugnazo&#x0304;</b> - <i>stoog-nad'-zo</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/G4767\">G4767</a>; to <i>render gloomy</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>glower</i> (<i>be overcast</i> with clouds, or <i>sombreness</i> of speech): - lower, be sad."}]}